President Obama has announced his intent to nominate several individuals to key administration posts. Allison Beck is nominated for Federal Mediation and Conciliation Director at the Federal Mediation and Conciliation Service. Brian James Egan is nominated for Legal Adviser at the Department of State. Eric Liu is nominated for Member of the Board of Directors of the Corporation for National and Community Service. Dallas Tonsager is nominated for Member of the Farm Credit Administration Board at the Farm Credit Administration. Maria Echaveste is nominated for Ambassador to the United Mexican States at the Department of State. Richard Rahul Verma is nominated for Ambassador to the Republic of India at the Department of State. Additionally, David Abney is appointed as a Member of the President's Export Council.